title: Vincent van Gogh Fishing in Spring, the Pont de Clichy (Asnières) Candle
description:
Candle developed from Vincent van Gogh’s Fishing in Spring, the Pont de Clichy (Asnières) (detail), 1887, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Add the glow of a masterpiece into your living space.

  • Size: 11 oz.
  • Dimensions: Box 5.4 x 4 x 4 in.  Candle 4.125 x 3.25 in.
  • Materials: 100% Soy, Glass, Box of Matches, Enviro-safe Wick.
  • Burn Time: 80 Hours
  • Scent: Cucumber, Crushed Garden Leaves
